{"tid":2276763,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"涉2.1億黑錢案 男警保釋","createTime":"2020-11-08T04:28:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T04:51:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8b1fbc20d842e0ef69bf0561ee7553b1f80b5146","tid":2276763,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T04:28:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201108/2E6AKIYEBFG5DI23MYHKVRUFHE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201108%2F2E6AKIYEBFG5DI23MYHKVRUFHE%2F&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft24aGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=e2880fb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201108%2F2E6AKIYEBFG5DI23MYHKVRUFHE%2F&h=7c674dd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201108/2E6AKIYEBFG5DI23MYHKVRUFHE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n涉2.1億黑錢案 男警保釋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/awjAWENthLDxhJgRtigekdg8iEA=/640x427/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YOUU3D74O5DVBGLFDB7A53D4EU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FawjAWENthLDxhJgRtigekdg8iEA%3D%2F640x427%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYOUU3D74O5DVBGLFDB7A53D4EU.jpg&h=e9a1e28d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■新界南總區警察總部<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方上周四拘捕八男三女，涉及2.1億洗黑錢案，包括新界南衝鋒隊23歲男警員。警方昨日表示，所有被捕男女均獲保釋，須於下月上旬向警方報到，而涉案警員已被停職。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n疑借出戶口洗其中2,200萬<br />\n<br />\n涉案被捕男警隸屬新界南總區衝鋒隊，加入警隊四年，據知案中他涉嫌借出戶口清洗約2,200萬元黑錢。毒品調查科財富。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，被捕人士涉嫌去年3月至今年10月處理共2.1億懷疑犯罪得益，所牽涉每個戶口交易金額由500至7,000萬不等。行動中，警方凍結相關銀行戶口約76萬元款項，又撿獲電話、手提電腦、銀行卡等證物。<br />\n<br />\n去年共有28名警員違紀被紀律處分，上周四一名九龍城分區24歲姓曾男警被捕，涉嫌藉模型單據騙取一名41歲男子2,100元。"},{"pid":"51020a85137a63be654f4ab92252f9fb40d9b8d5","tid":2276763,"uid":261873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T04:33:05.000Z","msg":"上庭前繼續出糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dfb1af7580526995762a8a87d63a04411866a4d","tid":2276763,"uid":33263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T04:49:29.000Z","msg":"2.1億洗錢可以保釋<br />\n但非法集結 就要即時收監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5b65965e6ada6739a150b8d651e33627feba102","tid":2276763,"uid":164497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T04:51:34.000Z","msg":"2.1億 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n仲可以保釋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後面有大粒佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}